.TH SUBARUCTL 1 "2025" "Subaru Control CLI"
.SH NAME
subaructl \- Subaru ECU/OBD unified CLI

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B subaructl
.IR COMMAND 
[ARGS]

.SH DESCRIPTION
Unified CLI for Subaru diagnostics, logging, dashboard, ECU patching.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --json
JSON output mode for machine-readable diagnostics.

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B doctor
Diagnostics (cmds/files/ports/groups/serial).

.TP
.B ssm-log
Start SSM CSV logger.

.TP
.B dash
Launch wrxdash Flask dashboard.

.TP
.B patch .IR BASELINE .IR TARGET
Generate safe ECU patch (--safety-check/flash-sim).

.TP
.B run .IR SERVICE
Run service: ssm-log, dash, patch, fastecu, dash-gui, obdai.

.TP
.B help
Show this help message.

.SH EXAMPLES
.B subaructl doctor
.br
.B subaructl doctor --json
.br
.B subaructl ssm-log
.br
.B subaructl run dash
.br
.B subaructl patch baseline.bin stage1.bin
.br
.B subaructl patch baseline.bin stage1.bin --safety-check

.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
SUBARU_SSM_PORT
Default: /dev/ttyACM0

.TP
SUBARU_ELM327_PORT
Default: /dev/rfcomm0

.TP
SUBARU_DASH_URL
Default: http://localhost:8080

.SH AUTHOR
BlackBOXAI

.SH "SEE ALSO"
.B run_all_help.sh(1),
ecuextractor/README.md
